  title: Magnificence in Marble
  description: My Pontiff, the statue is complete! Now we must merely decide where
    within the Ocularium it shall be placed. Whichever site we choose, we had best
    dispatch men to guard it. The more prominent the location, the greater its impact
    shall be, yet the higher the chances that a rival sect will seek to vandalize
    it.
